【Creative Gifts for Kids】Are you looking for gifts for boys and girls aged 1-3? LZZAPJ Suction Cup Spinning Toys are beautifully packaged, ideal for baby gifts, such as birthday gifts, Easter gifts, holiday gifts, Christmas gifts. Don't miss any chance to surprise your baby.

reviews.reviewText: we’ve had these for a few months and no issues until suddenly one of the balls broke out. my 9 month old was playing with it and thankfully we were sitting there with him when it popped out of the toy - could easily become a choking hazard. would advise supervision when baby/children are playing with these.i pulled and pushed the others to see if they pop out easily, but none others had the issue. We have no idea how it broke off - baby super strength i guess!
